      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_4_00033"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place">I Wollzeile 15</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_4_00034"/>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Richard.</salute> Ich bin heut beim <rs ref="#pmb42186" type="work">Doppel<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tmord</rs>, da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> im <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb34" type="place">Griensteidl</rs></hi>. Was morgen mit der <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00400-1"/><rs ref="#pmb40" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Josefstadt</hi></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00400-1">Am Nachmittag fand die Premiere des
                  Mimodramas <rs ref="#pmb30411" type="work">Der Buckelhans</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb42193" type="person">Pierre Blanchard de la Bretesche</rs>
                  statt.</note> los, wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s ich noch nicht; <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Hugo</rs> hat mir ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agt, d<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s er ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t.</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
